	"keywords": "Python, Web Development, Programming, Startup, Tech",
	"description": "Python is an incredibly versatile language. It’s considered to be a staple of\nmodern development. It’s used for the simplest of scripts to complex machine\nlearning and neural network training algorithms.\n\nBut perhaps the less-known usage of Python is its use as a web server.\nOvershadowed by more popular frameworks like as Node/Express and Ruby on Rails,\nPython is often overlooked as a web server choice for most developers.\n\nHaving a backend written in Python is really useful for several reasons,",
